These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, nigerian, german, thai
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, cooking, dancing, puzzles
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, september, july, april
4 different games are played: domino, poker, bridge, whist
City: boston, san-francisco, marseilles, nizza
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, marigold, lily, balloon-flower
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, plum, apricot, tomato
 1. the malaysian is the person playing domino##1
 2. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 6. the person eating pumpkin is the nigerian##1
 7. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 8. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 9. the person eating tomato is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
10. the person eating plum is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
11. the person who growsbellflower is the nigerian##1
12. the person eating plum is the person traveling to marseilles##1
13. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the thai##1
14. the person who growsmarigold is the thai##1
15. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who's birthday is in july##1
16. the malaysian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
17. the german is the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4      |
| Nationality      | malaysian       | thai      | german       | nigerian    |
| Hobby         | board-games    | puzzles    | cooking      | dancing    |
| Birthday           | april | november       | july | september     |
| Game   | domino         | bridge  | whist      | poker     |
| City   | san-francisco          | nizza     | marseilles       | boston |
| Flower         | lily       | marigold | balloon-flower       | bellflower   |
| Food     | tomato     | apricot  | plum         | pumpkin   |

