.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different games are played: bridge, go, backgammon, poker
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, may, february, march
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, milk, tea
City: venice, berlin, paris, new-york
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, indonesian, nigerian, pakistani
House: colonial, farmhouse, gothic-revival, futuristic
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, accountant, writer, manager
 1. the person playing poker is on the right of the manager##1
 2. the indonesian is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
 3. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 4. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 5. the person traveling to new-york is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the colonial house##1
 8. the person drinking milk is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 9. the australian is on the left of the pakistani##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
11. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
12. the pakistani is on the left of the accountant##1
13. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
14. the pilot is on the left of the colonial house##1
15. the futuristic house is on the far left##1
16. the pilot is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
17. the pakistani is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3      |      4      |
| Game          | backgammon     | go     | bridge      | poker  |
