10. the person drinking water is the person who growsmarigold##1
11. the chef is the person driving the helicopter##1
12. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person drinking water##1
13. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
14. the dancer is on the far left##1
15. the person who's birthday is in august is the victorian house##1
